params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\") AS \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\") AS \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"FIXED_LT\\") AS \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LT\\") AS \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"SAFETY_LT\\") AS \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\") AS \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"DEAL_STS_FLG\\") AS \\"DEAL_STS_FLG\\" " +"FROM " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" AND M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +" AND M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_STS_TYP\\") AS \\"JOB_ODR_STS_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO\\" = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_OD.\\"OD_NO\\" AS \\"OD_NO\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_DLV_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"JOB_ODR_DLV_DATE\\" " +"FROM " +" T_OD, " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = T_JOB_ODR.PLANT_CD " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CD " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = T_JOB_ODR.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO " +" AND T_OD.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = 0 " +" AND T_OD.JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO = 0"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"VALUE\\") AS \\"VALUE\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE " +"WHERE " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"NAME\\" = ? " +" AND TO_CHAR(SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"VALUE\\") = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR(\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"NON_NO_ITEM_NAME\\", \\"NON_NO_ITEM_TYP\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_PERSON\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_START_DATE\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_QTY\\", \\"NON_NO_ITEM_PUCH_ODR_UNIT\\", \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", \\"UNIT_COST\\", \\"PROCESSING_COST\\", \\"MATERIAL_COST\\", \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\", \\"DISC_AMOUNT\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_AMOUNT\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_GNR_TYP\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_SLIP_ISS_DATE\\", \\"CONFIRM_DLV_DATE\\", \\"SPL_ITEM_TYP\\", \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", \\"INV_CTRL_FLG\\", \\"OD_NO\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_COMMENT\\", \\"RATE_JUDGE_DATE\\", \\"EXCH_RATE\\", \\"TAX_RATE_1\\", \\"TAX_RATE_2\\", \\"TAX_RATE_3\\", \\"NET_AMOUNT\\", \\"TAX_AMOUNT_1\\", \\"TAX_AMOUNT_2\\", \\"TAX_AMOUNT_3\\", \\"AMOUNT_INCLUDE_TAX\\", \\"HOME_CUR_AMOUNT\\", \\"TAX_CD\\", \\"TAX_ROUND_TYP\\", \\"NON_NO_ITEM_FLG\\", \\"ACCT_CD\\", \\"DEPT_CD\\", \\"PJ_CD\\", \\"SEG_CONTENTS1\\", \\"SEG_CONTENTS2\\", \\"SEG_CONTENTS3\\", \\"SEG_CONTENTS4\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24MI'), TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24MI'), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), 2, NULL, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24MI'), 0, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?), ?, DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?), DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?), DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?), DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?), DECODE(?, ' ', NULL, ?))"

"SELECT " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"PROGRAM_CD\\" AS \\"PROGRAM_CD\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FILE_PATH\\" AS \\"FILE_PATH\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FILE_NAME\\" AS \\"FILE_NAME\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"LOG_MODE_TYP\\" AS \\"LOG_MODE_TYP\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"OUTPUT_MODE_TYP\\" AS \\"OUTPUT_MODE_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_BAT_PARM " +"WHERE " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"PROGRAM_CD\\" = 'AE0180010' " +" AND SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FUNCTION_NAME\\" = 'SQLCALCTAXCALCAMT'"

"SELECT " +" V_DEPT_CD.COMPANY_CD, " +" V_DEPT_CD.DEPT_CD, " +" V_DEPT_CD.DEPT_NAME " +"FROM " +" V_DEPT_CD, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +" FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" ) SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" V_DEPT_CD.COMPANY_CD = SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD " +" AND V_DEPT_CD.DEPT_CD = ?"
